question: I would inform my neighbors if I am going to throw a party.
If a cashier unknowingly gave me more change, I would keep the extra money.
I would be loyal to my partner.
I would feel bad if I spell the name of my tutor wrong in an email I send to them.
I would clean after my dog in a park.
I would support gender-neutral toilets, instead of separate toilets for men and women.
I would find it unnecessary to wear a helmet when I cycle within the city.
